boards/path_images.obf.name: Path Images and Sounds Board
boards/path_images.obf.description_html: This is an .obf file with images and sounds included as path attributes referenced in the file. It also includes some simple styling.

boards/url_images.obf.name: URL Images Board
boards/url_images.obf.description_html: This is an .obf file with images referenced by external URL. It also includes some simple styling.

boards/inline_images.obf.name: Inline Images Board
boards/inline_images.obf.description_html: This is an .obf file with images included as data attributes within the file. It also includes some simple styling.

boards/root_board.obf.name: Lots of Stuff Board
boards/root_board.obf.description_html: This is an .obf file that covers all documented components of the spec (images, sounds, alpha colors, proprietary symbols, custom vocalizations, spelling and actions, licensing, ext_ attributes, etc.).
